## Power Point 
### 01
* Data is all around use :  
  * Social media (Twitter, FaceBook,etc)
  * Streaming video (Netflix, Disney+, etc)
  * Emails (Google, Hotmail, etc)
  * Gaming (Steam, PlayStation, etc)
  * E-commerce (Amazon, Alibaba, etc)
  * etc

